{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SJKXzwLu6WuZ9pmGBAkHLj","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→HERB ROASTED PORK WITH MUSHROOMS : PORK WITH CARAMELIZED ONIONS (VARIATION)\n     2→\n     3→MAIN RECIPE: HERB ROASTED PORK WITH MUSHROOMS\n     4→\n     5→Ingredients:\n     6→\n     7→1.2kg pork shoulder or leg roast\n     8→500g mixed mushrooms (cremini, portobello, oyster), quartered\n     9→8 cloves garlic, crushed\n    10→4 sprigs fresh rosemary\n    11→4 sprigs fresh thyme\n    12→3 tbsp olive oil\n    13→200ml white wine\n    14→300ml chicken or pork stock\n    15→2 bay leaves\n    16→salt and pepper to taste\n    17→2 tbsp Dijon mustard\n    18→\n    19→Instructions:\n    20→\n    21→1. Preheat oven to 180°C.\n    22→2. Mix olive oil, mustard, crushed garlic, rosemary, thyme, salt, and pepper.\n    23→3. Rub generously all over the pork roast.\n    24→4. Heat a large roasting pan over medium-high heat. Brown the roast on all sides, about 10 minutes total.\n    25→5. Remove roast and set aside."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"06e30cc2-e666-4ba2-b79a-bd76ce637f9b","uuid":"0cf940a4-76e3-429d-a1bf-8ec7fe069f37","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/HERB ROASTED PORK WITH MUSHROOMS : PORK WITH CARAMELIZED ONIONS (VARIATION).generated.txt","content":"HERB ROASTED PORK WITH MUSHROOMS : PORK WITH CARAMELIZED ONIONS (VARIATION)\n\nMAIN RECIPE: HERB ROASTED PORK WITH MUSHROOMS\n\nIngredients:\n\n1.2kg pork shoulder or leg roast\n500g mixed mushrooms (cremini, portobello, oyster), quartered\n8 cloves garlic, crushed\n4 sprigs fresh rosemary\n4 sprigs fresh thyme\n3 tbsp olive oil\n200ml white wine\n300ml chicken or pork stock\n2 bay leaves\nsalt and pepper to taste\n2 tbsp Dijon mustard\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Preheat oven to 180°C.\n2. Mix olive oil, mustard, crushed garlic, rosemary, thyme, salt, and pepper.\n3. Rub generously all over the pork 