{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011vMkb2tfU1Pav9LXSDbaWE","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Lato | Zupy | DLA 4 OSÓB | PRZYGOTOWANIE 15 MIN | GOTOWANIE 20 MIN\n     2→\n     3→OGÓRKOWA ZUPA\n     4→\n     5→Ogórkowa zupa, or Polish cucumber soup, is a refreshing summer soup served\n     6→either hot or cold. The dill-infused broth is bright and tangy, perfect for\n     7→warm days when you want something light yet satisfying and nourishing.\n     8→\n     9→INGREDIENTS:\n    10→- 6 medium cucumbers, peeled and diced\n    11→- 6 cups vegetable or chicken stock\n    12→- 1 large onion, diced\n    13→- 2 tbsp butter\n    14→- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n    15→- 3 tbsp fresh dill, chopped\n    16→- 2 tbsp fresh lemon juice\n    17→- 1/2 cup sour cream\n    18→- 1/4 tsp white pepper\n    19→- Salt to taste\n    20→- Fresh dill sprigs for garnish"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"06e30cc2-e666-4ba2-b79a-bd76ce637f9b","uuid":"f62fbd7e-b545-41a5-8731-8c24d3ddb6b6","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Ogórkowa Zupa.generated.txt","content":"Lato | Zupy | DLA 4 OSÓB | PRZYGOTOWANIE 15 MIN | GOTOWANIE 20 MIN\n\nOGÓRKOWA ZUPA\n\nOgórkowa zupa, or Polish cucumber soup, is a refreshing summer soup served\neither hot or cold. The dill-infused broth is bright and tangy, perfect for\nwarm days when you want something light yet satisfying and nourishing.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 6 medium cucumbers, peeled and diced\n- 6 cups vegetable or chicken stock\n- 1 large onion, diced\n- 2 tbsp butter\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n- 3 tbsp fresh dill, chopped\n- 2 tbsp fresh lemon juice\n- 1/2 cup sour cream\n- 1/4 tsp white pepper\n- Salt to taste\n- Fresh dill sprigs for garnish","numLines":20,"startLine":1,"totalLines":37}}}
