{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Lt1jsRLTVmofMZWKLT4X8x","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→2 large sweet potatoes, peeled and cut into 2cm cubes\n     2→4 cups fresh spinach leaves\n     3→½ red onion, thinly sliced\n     4→½ cup roasted walnuts, roughly chopped\n     5→¼ cup dried cranberries\n     6→½ cup crumbled goat cheese or feta\n     7→\n     8→For dressing:\n     9→3 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil\n    10→1½ tablespoons balsamic vinegar\n    11→1 tablespoon maple syrup\n    12→1 teaspoon Dijon mustard\n    13→Salt and pepper to taste\n    14→\n    15→Method:\n    16→Preheat oven to 200°C. Toss sweet potato cubes with olive oil, salt, and pepper. Spread on\n    17→baking tray in single layer. Roast for 25-30 minutes until golden and tender, stirring halfway\n    18→through cooking time.\n    19→\n    20→While potatoes roast, whisk together dressing ingredients in small bowl until emulsified."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"06e30cc2-e666-4ba2-b79a-bd76ce637f9b","uuid":"fdb5b2a9-e2e5-4f1f-9ac8-7d279f64b212","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Sweet Potato Salad.generated.txt","content":"2 large sweet potatoes, peeled and cut into 2cm cubes\n4 cups fresh spinach leaves\n½ red onion, thinly sliced\n½ cup roasted walnuts, roughly chopped\n¼ cup dried cranberries\n½ cup crumbled goat cheese or feta\n\nFor dressing:\n3 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil\n1½ tablespoons balsamic vinegar\n1 tablespoon maple syrup\n1 teaspoon Dijon mustard\nSalt and pepper to taste\n\nMethod:\nPreheat oven to 200°C. Toss sweet potato cubes with olive oil, salt, and pepper. Spread on\nbaking tray in single layer. Roast for 25-30 minutes until golden and tender, stirring halfway\nthrough cooking time.\n\nWhile potatoes roast, whisk together dressing ingredients in small bowl until emulsified.","numLines":20,"startLine":1,"totalLines":58}}}
