lonka\" has only 1 word and may be rejected by `isLikelyGarbled` (single word with ≤3 unicode letters? No, \"Golonka\" has 7 letters). Let me check — wordCount=1, and it's not in NON_TITLE_WORDS. The issue might be that \"Golonka\" scores poorly on embeddings and gets beaten by section headers deeper in the file."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1142,"cache_read_input_tokens":70782,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1142},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"06e30cc2-e666-4ba2-b79a-bd76ce637f9b","uuid":"e5cadb0b-3003-432a-96fb-992708a108ad"}
