{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":303072,"duration_api_ms":290992,"num_turns":26,"result":"The improvement plan is written. Here's a brief overview of the key proposals:\n\n**The big architectural change**: Move OCR repair *before* candidate scoring instead of after. A dictionary-guided repair function (~500 food words) resolves ambiguous digit→letter substitutions (`1→l` vs `1→i`) by checking which substitution produces a real word. This fixes Patterns 1, 2, and 7 (10 of 18 failures).\n\n**Structural fixes**:\n- **Pattern 3** (3 failures): Switch position bonus from raw-line-position to candidate-relative-position, so the first candidate after filtered preamble lines (category headers, metadata) gets proper priority.\n- **Pattern 4** (2 failures): Detect title-absent pages (first 3 lines are all ingredients/instructions) and return empty instead of guessing.\n- **Pattern 5** (2 failures): Protect compound titles (containing ` : ` or ` + `) from the \"shorter substring wins\" dedup rule.\n- **Pattern 6** (1 failure): Detect bilingual layout pattern (short title + English subtitle + Ingredients:) and boost the short title. Also expand the cooking-verb filter list.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"06e30cc2-e666-4ba2-b79a-bd76ce637f9b","total_cost_usd":1.28739115,"usage":{"input_tokens":16,"cache_creation_input_tokens":70377,"cache_read_input_tokens":723591,"output_tokens":11194,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":70377,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":16,"outputTokens":11194,"cacheReadInputTokens":723591,"cacheCreationInputTokens":70377,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.08158175,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":835,"outputTokens":3171,"cacheReadInputTokens":305419,"cacheC